data.text:
Mark Thomas Neves was born on 14 May 1976, in Walnut Creek, Contra Costa, California, United States. He lived in San Antonio, Bexar, Texas, United States in 1999 and Santa Clara, California, United States in 2005. He died on 5 June 2011, at the age of 35, and was buried in Newcastle, Placer, California, United States.
